From Dana:

- Grate a whole cucumber and remove as much liquid as you desire for overall sauce thickness
- Combine:
- Aforementioned cucumber
- 2 cups full fat plain greek yogurt (a little less is okay)
- 2 tbsp olive oil
- 2 tbsp dried dill
- 1 tsbp lemon juice
- 1-2 cloves minced garlic
- 1/2 tsp sea salt

Dana says it was good
